By Boyuan Zhang

Simple 2D Shooter created in C# with the MonoGame framework

Video Demo 1.0: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0p0Z2zJZK4I
Video Demo 2.0: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1dARkSlBPuM

KEYS:
Up arrow - Move Up
Down arrow - Move Down 
left arrow - rotate counter-clockwise
right arrow - rotate clockwise
space - shoot
Z key - zoom in
X key - zoom out
C key - rotate camera counter-clockwise
V key - rotate camera clockwise


- Project was started for learning purposes of Graphics programming and the MonoGame framework

- Attempting to structure code in a way that will make future development / maintenance on this project as smoothe as possible.

